name: Blakean Party
description:
This NFT is a digital cyber-revision of William's Blake painting "The Body of Abel Found by Adam and Eve".

The motivation for create such piece was integrate traditional painting hues with 3d vaporwave figures and hand painted flickering drawn lines to create and electronic vibe where the mystical mood of the blake painting is melt with the digital graphical interventions.

The track belongs to my noise-sound experimental project Ra-Sunt V.

Production date: 2019
